Kimwe mu bintu bihambaye kuruta ibindi muri uwo mugwi ni impinduro ya Google yahinduwe hakoreshejwe itabi, ivyo bikaba bituma impinduro zishobora guhindurwa hanze y’itabi zimaze kwimurwa amakuru ajanye n’ururimi umuntu yipfuza.
Gukoresha telefone ngendanwa yawe birashobora kuba bwo buryo bworoshe kandi bworoshe kuruta ubundi bwo gukoresha igihe uvuye mu gihugu cawe c’amavukiro.
Irashobora kuziganya amahera ku bijanye no kugura amakarata mashasha akoreshwa mu guhingura imashini yitwa GPS, canke igikoresho citwa GPS canke gukotesha imodoka.
Nimba udafise amakuru ajanye na telefone yawe, canke igihe itaba ihari, ivyo bakora birashobora kuba bike canke bidashobora kuboneka.
Mu mangazini yose yo mw’ifuriro, usanga huzuyemwo udukarata tw’amatelefone dushobora gukoreshwa biciye ku matelefone y’umushahara canke kuri telefone zisanzwe.
Naho amakarata menshi ari meza mu bijanye no guhamagara aho ari ho hose, ayandi makarata amwamwe arafasha mu guha urukaratasi rubereye imigwi kanaka y’ibihugu.
Ivyo bikorwa akenshi usanga biciye ku nomero z’amatelefone zishobora guhamagarwa mu matelefone menshi ata co zitwaye.
Amategeko ajanye n’ugufata amafoto ubudahorereza arakora kandi ku bijanye n’amavidewo yafashwe amajwi, bikaba bishoboka mbere ko arushiriza kuba ayahambaye.
Nimba gusa ufashe ifoto y’ikintu utemewe, ntukwiye kwiyumvira n’ukugifata.
Nimba ukoresha akabuyenge, nusuzume imbere y’igihe ivyo urekuriwe kuraba be n’ivyo usabwa gukora canke ibindi bikoresho.
Gutwara agatebe hafi y’indege canke mw’isinzi ry’abantu nka bose ni iciyumviro kibi, naho coba kitemewe n’amategeko mu karere iwanyu.
Muri iki gihe, ingendo z’indege usanga ari gake cane zikoreshwa mu ndege zitabanje kurondera no kugereranya ibiciro vyazo.
Rimwe na rimwe, iyo ndege nyene irashobora kuba ifise ibiciro bitandukanye cane ku bahinga batandukanye kandi igafasha cane mu kugereranya ibiva mu kurondera no mu kuraba ku muhora w’iyo ndege ubwayo imbere y’uko ironka ibitabu.
Naho bitoba ngombwa ko uronka urupapuro rw’iragi kugira ngo ugende gatoyi mu bihugu bimwebimwe nk’ingenzi canke w’urudandaza, kujayo uri umunyeshure mpuzamakungu mu bisanzwe bisaba ko umara umwanya muremure kuruta kujayo nk’uw’ingenzi asanzwe.
Muri rusangi, kuguma mu gihugu ico ari co cose co mu mahanga mu kiringo kirekire bizosaba ko uronka urupapuro rw’iragi imbere y’igihe.
Muri rusangi, impapuro z’umunyeshure zirafise ivyo zisabwa be n’uburyo butandukanye zikoreshwa n’ingenzi zisanzwe canke impapuro z’ivy’ubucuruzi.
Mu bihugu vyinshi, uzokenera ikete rivuye ku muhari wipfuza kwiga, be n’ikimenyamenya c’amahera agufasha kwibeshaho n’imiburiburi mu mwaka wa mbere w’ingendo yawe.
Niwihweze iyo ntunganyo, hamwe n’ikigo gijejwe ivyo kwimukira mu gihugu wipfuza kwiga ibintu vy’ido n’ido bisabwa.
Utabaye umumenyeshamakuru, gukorera mu mahanga muri rusangi bisobanura ko uzobwirizwa kuriha amakori y’amahera mu gihugu ubamwo.
Amakori y’amakori atangwa mu bihugu bitandukanye usanga atunganijwe mu buryo butandukanye, kandi igitigiri c’amakori be n’imigwi y’amakori usanga bitandukanye cane.
Mu bihugu bimwebimwe, nk’akarorero Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika na Kanada, abantu barasaba ikori ry’amahera ku rwego rw’igihugu no ku rugero rw’aho baba, akaba ari co gituma igitigiri c’amatagisi be n’amasandugu bishobora gutandukana bivanye n’intara n’intara.
Naho ubushakashatsi bujanye n’ivyo kwimukira mu gihugu c’amavukiro akenshi usanga ata ho bugarukira canke ugaheza umwuga igihe ushitse mu gihugu cawe c’amavukiro, gucungera imigenzo birashobora kuba ikintu kigoye.
Nurabe neza ko uzi ivyo ushoboye be n’ivyo udashobora kuzana no kuvuga ikintu na kimwe ku mategeko.
